name: BXL POSTER
description:
Poster based on my "BXL" algorithm. 

I can send to the owners the orignal version of 8268 × 11811px to print a huge poster of 70x100cm (27 by 39 inches)

Digital size : 2000×2857px

BXL is a generative piece creating a digital painting effect clipped in a circle.
The size, position and motion frequency of each trails are generated by code (Javascript).

Created by Quentin Hocdé, in Brussels (Belgium).
